kovo station the person was in between two cars of the train attempting to climb up an object in the shape of a pipe that is attached to one of the cars. As they were doing this they fell under the train and subsequently died.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.netall.ru/transport/news/1038529.html|title=13-year-old hooker died in the fall from the \"Swallows\"|date=9 April 2019|work=Infoportal Zelenograd|access-date=31 January 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"Inforportal Zelenograd 9 April 2018\">{{Cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EAt96YfWVD4|title=Fall of the hook from the Swallow in Podrezkovo|date=9 April 2018|work=Infoportal Zelenograd|access-date=31 January 2020}}</ref><ref name=newsmir18march2019 />\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://iz.ru/730063/2018-04-09/zatceper-podrostok-pogib-pod-moskvoi|title=Zatseper teenager died near Moscow|date=9 April 2019|work=Izvestia|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ren.tv/news/v-rossii/291790-sk-nachal-proverku-posle-gibeli-13-letnego-zatsepera-pod-moskvoi|title=SK began checking after the death of a 13-year-old catcher near Moscow|date=9 April 2018|work=REN|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n|-\n|{{dts|May 2018}} \n|Russia - Moscow \n|Died\n|Unconfirmed \n|\n|A person, 16, was on the roof of a train travelling from Moscow to Nakhabino. They were at one point killed and they body was later found. They had in their possesion a video camera and other equipment.\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://iz.ru/739918/2018-05-06/v-moskve-pogib-snimavshii-video-na-kryshe-elektrichki-shkolnik|title=A schoolboy filming a video on the roof of a train was killed in Moscow|date=6 May 2018|work=Izvestia|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n|-\n|{{dts|14 May 2018}} \n|Russia - Moscow \n|Died\n|Hit by train \n|\n|A person, 15, was with two other people on a train going from Moscow-Kievskaya station to Solnechnaya station. The 15 year old put on some gloves, accessed the intercar space and climbed onto the roof of the train w